genre_psd: PSD-GENRE: Internal Logic Displacement â€” The absurd follows rules that aren't ours but are internally consistent. Characters treat the impossible as inconvenient, not wondrous. Tone precision: the ordinary and the impossible coexist at the same volume. The surreal reveals what realism can't reach.
genre_nsd: NSD-GENRE: Anti-Random Surreal â€” Randomness is not surrealism. "Weird things happening" without internal logic is incoherence with a writing degree. Characters reacting with whimsy instead of realistic frustration. Dream logic as excuse for narrative laziness. Quirky is not surreal.
genre_nsd_focus: Consistent internal logic over decorative randomness
