genre_psd: PSD-GENRE: Discipline as Architecture â€” Martial skill shown through cost, training, and physical limitation. Social hierarchy visible in gesture, address, and seating. Philosophy embedded in action and choice, not monologue. Cultural specificity in daily texture: food, protocol, weather, trade routes. Combat as conversation.
genre_nsd: NSD-GENRE: Anti-Orientalist Fantasy â€” Generic "ancient Eastern wisdom" with no specific cultural grounding. Martial arts as magic system instead of physical discipline with real cost. Characters who monologue philosophy mid-fight. Honorifics sprinkled for flavor without understanding the social structure they encode. White-robed sages dispensing fortune cookies.
genre_nsd_focus: Cultural specificity over orientalist decoration
